<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Orçamento Empresarial</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary-color: #0f172a;
        --primary-light: #1e293b;
        --accent-color: #3b82f6;
        --accent-light: #60a5fa;
        --success-color: #22c55e;
        --warning-color: #f59e0b;
        --danger-color: #ef4444;
        --text-color: #334155;
        --text-light: #64748b;
        --border-color: #e2e8f0;
        --background-light: #f8fafc;
        --card-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
          0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text-color);
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: white;
        box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        position: relative;
      }

      .header-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .company-info {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .company-info h1 {
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: white;
      }

      .company-details {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }

      .document-info {
        background-color: var(--primary-light);
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .document-number {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .document-date {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }

      .main-content {
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .info-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .info-card {
        background-color: var(--background-light);
        border-radius: 1px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }

      .info-card h3 {
        color: var(--primary-color);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
      }

      .info-group {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .info-item {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--text-light);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--primary-color);
      }

      .itens-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: separate;
        border-spacing: 0;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .itens-table th {
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        padding: 1rem;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .itens-table td {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      }

      .itens-table tbody tr:hover {
        background-color: var(--background-light);
      }

      .price-column {
        text-align: right;
        font-family: "Monaco", "Courier New", monospace;
      }

      .totais {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        background-color: var(--background-light);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .total-card {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        min-width: 300px;
      }

      .total-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
      }

      .total-final {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--primary-color);
        font-weight: bold;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .status-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .status-ativo {
        background-color: #dcfce7;
        color: #166534;
      }

      .rodape {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .rodape-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .rodape-section h4 {
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .rodape-section p {
        color: #94a3b8;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      @media print {
        body {
          background-color: white;
          padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
          box-shadow: none;
        }

        .header,
        .rodape {
          -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
          print-color-adjust: exact;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body {
          padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .info-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .rodape-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .header-content {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .document-info {
          margin-top: 1rem;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
          <div class="company-info">
            <h1>Orçamento</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="document-info">
            <div class="document-number">
              Orçamento Nº <%= orcamento.codigo_orcamento %>
            </div>
            <div class="document-date">
              Emitido em <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('pt-BR') %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="main-content">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Informações do Cliente</h3>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Nome</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= orcamento.cliente.nome %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Código</div>
                <div class="info-value">
                  <%= orcamento.cliente.codigo_cliente %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">CPF</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= orcamento.cliente.cpf %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">RG</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= orcamento.cliente.rg %></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Email</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= orcamento.cliente.email %></div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Status</div>
                <div class="status-badge status-ativo">
                  <%= orcamento.cliente.status %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Endereço</h3>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Endereço</div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Número</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Bairro</div>
                <div class="info-value"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Cidade</div>
                <div class="info-value"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-group">
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">CEP</div>
                <div class="info-value"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Estado</div>
                <div class="info-value"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <table class="itens-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Descrição</th>
              <th>Quantidade</th>
              <th>Preço Unitário</th>
              <th>Subtotal</th>
              <th>Total</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% orcamento.itens.forEach((item) => { %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= item.descricao %></td>
              <td><%= item.quantidade %></td>
              <td class="price-column">
                R$ <%= item.preco_unitario.toFixed(2) %>
              </td>
              <td class="price-column">
                R$ <%= item.subtotal_unitario.toFixed(2) %>
              </td>
              <td class="price-column">
                R$ <%= item.total_unitario.toFixed(2) %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <% }); %>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="totais">
          <div class="total-card">
            <div class="total-row">
              <span>Subtotal:</span>
              <span
                >R$ <%= orcamento.valores.subtotal?.toFixed(2) || '0.00'
                %></span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
              <span>Desconto(%)</span>
              <span
                >R$ <%= orcamento.valores.desconto_percentual_total?.toFixed(2)
                || '0.00' %></span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
              <span>Desconto:</span>
              <span
                >R$ <%= orcamento.valores.desconto_valor__total?.toFixed(2)||
                '0.00' %></span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="total-final">
              <span>Total:</span>
              <span
                >R$ <%= orcamento.valores.total?.toFixed(2) || '0.00' %></span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>

      <footer class="rodape">
        <div class="rodape-grid">
          <div class="rodape-section">
            <h4>Condições</h4>
            <p>
              Este orçamento tem validade de 7 dias a partir da data de emissão.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rodape-section">
            <h4>Contato</h4>
            <p>
              Em caso de dúvidas, entre em contato conosco:<br />
              Telefone: (XX) XXXX-XXXX<br />
              Email: contato@empresa.com.br<br />
              Horário: Seg. a Sex. das 8h às 18h
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rodape-section">
            <h4>Informações Adicionais</h4>
            <p>
              Forma de pagamento a combinar.<br />
              Prazo de entrega: conforme disponibilidade.<br />
              Frete não incluso.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
          "
        >
          <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Empresa LTDA. Todos os direitos
            reservados.<br />
            CNPJ: XX.XXX.XXX/0001-XX
          </p>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
